AuthorName: Gnagna Thioye
AuthorCountry: Senegal
Text: Tukish is rich of architectural monument and blue mosque where the attraction
  of tourist is huge.They are very open people and islamic who concentrated their
  activities in Istanbul .Turks prefer to do business with those they know and respect,
  therefore spend time establishing a personal relationship.In the summer, and especially
  in the cities of Istanbul, Izmir and Anakara the weather is very hot and humid.the
  Nazar Boncugu, also known as the evil eye is in offices, homes, in transport and
  businessesand Its the talisman they use  for protection. Breakfast is the most important
  meal of the day and typically includes eggs, cucumbers, tomatoes, and olives but
  never forget the bread, at either breakfast or other mealtimes with tea .The Eyup
  area of Istanbul is slowly growing in popularity as increasingly more tourists and
  property buyers look towards the neighbourhood that has shed its past mistakes and
  reinvented itself as a desirable place to live and work.Istanbul is the heart of
  turkey all businesses are concentrated ;people are in activity all the day .
